@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ztsbpa(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (v1 / wp.abs(v0))
    v0 = (0.16 - tmp)
    tmp = v0
    v2 = (wp.abs((v0 + 0.97 - v0 + 0.70)) + tmp)
    tmp = 0.99
    v0 = wp.sin(v1)
    data[tid] = v0
